Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inside of the heart is a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stars and snow are all around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The vase is the cornerstone of the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Within the boundary of the crime scene, what will the culprit do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look like a child, but have the intellect of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Uncle refused a case to find Morita Hideo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Detective Boys stepped in to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While we were searching for the watch in his apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:02:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idetsuki Eiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, manager of the apartment complex, barged in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And began watching a movie in the audio room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After some searching, we found the lost watch in the washing machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We heard the sound of something breaking coming from the audio room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we ran to find the source of the noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We discovered Idetsuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} lying dead on the floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Killed by blunt trauma to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, Morita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he has an alibi that we can confirm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just how could he have done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's not the only thing that's troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that someone is checking up on Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They all disappeared from police headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reports from cases that Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has solved up until now have been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know when they went missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see, I think it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the day you guys were involved in that busjacking incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, their target isn't Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one they're aiming for...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Forgotten Memento from the Crime\N(Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:38.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Forgotten Memento from the Crime:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Part 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi, what did Detective Takagi say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't tell us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid, how are you any different?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Shinichi? Are you really hiding something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without considering the consequences, you pursue truth and justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The burdens you bear are yours alone because you feel obligated to protect those around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dangerous, boy-like personality is so painfully and achingly intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That that pure scent of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is strangling me, her, and yourself with loneliness, uncertainty, and vulnerability.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you smell something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, it smells like something's burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be coming from the microwave right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right, it's coming from in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there"s nothing inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These... Aren't these dry flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or rather, they may have been thrown out because they all dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, it must be somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something that big shouldn't be this hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be in another room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are still sandwiches left!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can eat them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:45.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you sure eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I suspected, it was a trick after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, in the audio room..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, I forgot my paper airplane in this room when I was playing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Behind that curtain above the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please get it, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, I'll get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I thought he was smart, but I guess he's just a normal kid after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, it's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see a paper plane anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh wow, there are so many appliances!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing? Hurry and get him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you sure have a lot of VCRs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I don't use them anymore, I put them all up on the shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come down, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What Idetsuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had no idea it would be her last movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or that it would be a cruel story...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They didn't say anything about going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I told them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? What did the inspector say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He thinks it's an interesting theory, so he's going to help us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's your turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do exactly what I told you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just keep worrying and worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about your precious girlfriend, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what Detective Takagi told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't lose your grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mustn't tell her about your true identity or the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:31.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since you're a boy, I can tell that you're happy to have received her chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid, I'm not happy at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since, after so long, I haven't told her anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Shinichi, you did accept Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s chocolate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you must've, in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She would want to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I told her how I feel, she'd just miss me even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm the guy who's been breaking her heart by making her wait an eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm always by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see her cry anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it means that I no longer have a place in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems pretty immature of me, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pitiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? There's something that's been stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really, really sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something weird is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit's real motive must've been a burglary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please come to the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Morita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what is it that's been stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not a whole bowl—just the bottom of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other ones in that stack have a bottom, but this one doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was like that when I bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a defective item.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What's ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'd be so kind, Morita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a simple, on-site investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's go to the audio room where Idetsuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Original Broadcast Date:\NMarch 4th, 2002\N\NBased on manga:\NVol. 33 Files 7-9
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's turned on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The VCR is turned on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is there anything wrong with the VCRs on the shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's not the VCRs, it's the video tapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had to move them there for a while—there are just so many...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, Idetsuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} rewound the tape after watching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, when she was about to take it out of the VCR, she was attacked from behind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's re-enact the whole incident using the VCR.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you can be the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for the victim... Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, could I ask you to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, I'll be the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idetsuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} often watched videos here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's better if I do it, since I know the room better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's a good point!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, please do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, she inserted the tape into this very bottom VCR...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Second, she sat down to watch the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, when the movie ended, she rewound the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please rewind the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the tape was rewinding, the culprit lurked behind her from the entrance, holding the vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the tape finished rewinding and the victim was about to take the tape from the VCR...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit raised the vase, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please hurry and take out the tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why aren't you using the remote?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the remote you're holding has an eject button on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:27.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll eject it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The video tapes aren't going to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We changed the code number of the VCR on the shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Basically, Morita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is how you committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You programmed your VCRs so that the one on the bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as the one on the shelf...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would be controlled by a single remote.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You placed a tape into the top VCR.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, you set the vase filled with water and flowers in front of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, to make sure the vase would tip over, you had it balanced halfway on top of another video tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, you closed the curtain and the trick was complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, using the movie that Idetsuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had been looking for as bait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You lured her into this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you had to do then was to ask her to eject the tape and give it back when she was finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she went to eject the tape with the remote...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tape in the top VCR came out as well, tipped over the vase...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And caused it to fall on her while she was reaching for the tape in the bottom VCR.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's possible for you to have set up this trap because she comes here frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could easily predict the timing of her actions after she ejected the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, the top VCR has a function which automatically reinserts the tape if its opening is obstructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if the tape had sounds prerecorded onto it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would automatically start playing after the tape was reinserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Immediately after the vase fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We heard sounds of a person running and the front door slamming...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making it seem as though the crime was committed by an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could hear it very clearly because she had turned the volume up very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason for using the very bottom VCR...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was to lengthen the falling distance of the vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, you had a timer set up to turn off the power of the top VCR...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that the police wouldn't get suspicious when they opened the curtain. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've just re-enacted the clever trick that you used.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The vase in the entryway was..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These bowls!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You glued them together like a sandwich and placed them at the entrance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While you were making sandwiches...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You secretly took these bowls to the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hid them together with the other bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is one of the flowers that was in the vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You threw it out after drying it up in the microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your wife even arranged these flowers for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poor flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife didn't arrange those flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman sent them to me on the day of my wife's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was already so broke that I couldn't afford the same flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because of stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman urged my wife to trade stocks behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result of her massive debt, my wife was driven to her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then her accident was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She jumped in front of a car the day after she told me about the stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:29.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She left me only a letter, with that watch wrapped inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wrote, "This is the one thing I don't want to get broken, so I'll leave it with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could care less about those flowers from that despicable woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll discuss the rest down at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still, I pity those flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would have been so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they didn't even have a chance to bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making them die so early is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flowers are fragile and ephemeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how well you protect them from the wind or the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if there is a fence all around them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:26.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The flowers will die without sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fence has no chance against a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're aware of that, Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why isn't anyone answering?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:18:59.51,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Please stop trying to catch me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:03.18,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,There you are, my dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dinnertime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must be upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ingredients have been abandoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the TV in the office wasn't turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,t seems that someone is checking up on Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that guy have...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess who?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad hit the jackpot in a horse race.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,J-Jackpot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was so excited that he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We're having steak tonight! Go get beef and sake!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:22:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I dropped everything in the middle of cooking and ran out to buy it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the best and freshest meat always runs out quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did Uncle go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably bragging about it to the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make a steak that's as delicious as a five-star restaurant's.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:28.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.89,0:22:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man with the black wool hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might be someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.90,0:22:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blacken the meat, but please don't burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:22:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not! Leave it all to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no way Ran would know him.
